  "message": "chore(cargo): Add exclude patterns for crate publishing\n\nExcludes development artifacts, planning docs, and temporary files\nfrom crates.io package to reduce download size:\n- Images (*.png, *.webp)\n- Planning/progress docs (AGENTS.md, PLAN_*, etc.)\n- Beads tracking files (.beads/)\n- Build artifacts (target-*, a.out)\n- Scripts directory\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
